# vector-floorplan-ai conventions

- Read `AGENTS.md` at the start of substantial tasks; **do not edit it unless the user asks**.
- Code lives in `src/vector_floorplan_ai/`; tests in `tests/` (concise unit tests).
- Output target is **IFC**, not raster images or vendor-locked formats.
- Run `make lint` and `make test` before finishing Python changes.
- Minimize scope; match existing patterns; no commits unless requested.
